  "3134220": {
    "name": "收获之旅 试玩版",
    "steam_appid": 3134220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的区长父亲为了锻炼你，稍微动用了一些手段，让你成为黑石矿洞21区的管理者，并为你定了一个小目标：赚一个亿。你需要努力经营21区，并想方设法从冒险者那里赚取金钱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《收获之旅》是一款俯视角模拟经营建造游戏，融合种植、自动化、冒险、塔防战斗元素。游戏围绕“<i><strong>冒险采集-基地加工-商品贩卖</strong></i>”模式进行。玩家前往矿洞冒险，收集各类资源，回到基地后将其加工并贩卖，并挑战最终的小目标。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>冒险采集-回合&amp;塔防&amp;组合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要保护<strong>采矿机</strong>免受敌人的攻击，在每个回合开始前，建造好围墙、防御炮塔、防御设施，同时武器上膛准备迎战四面八方进攻的敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/f5afa68ad5739871d36022ad58870bdf.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/f5afa68ad5739871d36022ad58870bdf.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着等级的提升，你将解锁更多种类的炮塔，玩家可以自由组合它们，并将其特殊属性进行融合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/a8c19758d6abb80a7fbab060de78231f.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/a8c19758d6abb80a7fbab060de78231f.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过快速设置界面，简化游戏操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/80e2201a6f38a6f66c3f3e26913fd107.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/80e2201a6f38a6f66c3f3e26913fd107.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基地加工-自动化&amp;神奇道具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了达成快速赚取一个亿的小目标，玩家可以将冒险采集得到的资源进行加工，就可以让其价值增加。基于这个原理，组装一条自动化生产线，并等待一些时间就可以制造出很多物品。什么？不想等的太久？在游戏中快速睡一觉，等待第二天的到来就可以了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/9db1346c612f4daa82a99f81901a6712.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/9db1346c612f4daa82a99f81901a6712.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着等级的提升，你会发现越来越多的神奇道具，这些道具可以帮你解决很多麻烦，例如让植物快速生长、让区域内的时间快速流动或者时间停止……善加利用他们，让你事半功倍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/5ccb289de02003d4005ddfaefef52565.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/5ccb289de02003d4005ddfaefef52565.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/5ccb289de02003d4005ddfaefef52565.mp4?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>商品贩卖-商品&amp;行情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着等级提升，可开发的商品将会越来越多，选择合适的时机，卖出这些商品，可收获更高的利润。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/f003ad1d163330ca4d235043b9861daa.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/f003ad1d163330ca4d235043b9861daa.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>冒险者-雇佣&amp;战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你对采集资源这件事感到一丝疲惫，可以雇佣冒险者小队前往矿洞去采集，虽然采集任务凶多吉少，但我们通过一些政策，让挂掉的冒险者资金充公</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/42a6abc209ecb3d7b9f3e28219ff70a7.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/42a6abc209ecb3d7b9f3e28219ff70a7.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基地-建设&amp;发展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以在地表建造大型专属房间，研究科技、研发商品、生产设备机器，也可以种植各类作物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/fd11a8cd72f70b552155cc95a729f78d.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/fd11a8cd72f70b552155cc95a729f78d.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署各种设备、机械臂、传送带实现自动化生产。玩家也可以在地下建造高效率的设施，生产各类基础资源、加工资源等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/916e419b1482919a3eba4f010910891a.poster.avif?t=1740365935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134220/extras/916e419b1482919a3eba4f010910891a.webm?t=1740365935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
